WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:11.360 --> 00:00:14.160
"I'm Trishna Dey.
I'm 14 years old.

00:00:14.960 --> 00:00:20.720
"When I grow up I dream of being a footballer.
After my studies I want to be an airhostess.

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:37.920
"When I was asked to play football,
I was very scared.

00:00:37.920 --> 00:00:41.240
"But when I went to the pitch
with my elder sister,

00:00:41.240 --> 00:00:44.400
"the coach was very
encouraging of me to play.

00:00:45.040 --> 00:00:49.480
"Other than football, I also practice Karate,
and learn English.

00:00:49.480 --> 00:00:52.880
"My confidence has gone up
from being able to speak English.

00:00:54.520 --> 00:01:05.240
"By playing football my daugthers
learn more about the world

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:17.520
"I have loved playing football
since I was a kid.

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:23.880
"But before our small pitch couldn't fit
every kid who wanted to play.

00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:28.640
"When we have questions
about the game,

00:01:28.640 --> 00:01:33.040
"we go to our coach and
he helps us to understand.

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:39.400
"We help the kids to study" 

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:44.520
"and stand on their own feet, earn money,
and take care of their family and society.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.280
"I'm very excited." 

00:01:54.280 --> 00:02:01.560
"The FIFA World Cup which nobody
can view easily and I will get to see it !

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:04.880
"I'm very lucky and very happy !" 

00:02:12.600 --> 00:02:16.920
"This is the FIFA World Cup trophy." 

